extends layout

block content
  .container
    .row.page-header
      .col-lg-12.text-center
        h1(style="color: white;") Welcome to the World of Data Science
        p Explore the Fascinating World of Data and Analytics
      
      .col-lg-6.text-center
        img(src="https://imageio.forbes.com/specials-images/imageserve/615a844b0e678d9d11c5fc26/0x0.jpg?format=jpg&width=1200", alt="Data Science Illustration", style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;")

    .row.about-data-science
      .col-lg-6
        h2(style="color: white;") What is Data Science?
        p.large-font
          | Data Science is an interdisciplinary field that combines domain knowledge, programming skills, and statistical analysis to extract meaningful insights and patterns from data. It involves collecting, cleaning, and analyzing data to make informed decisions and predictions.

    .row.data-science-jobs
      .col-lg-12
        h2(style="color: white;") Career Opportunities in Data Science
        p.large-font
          | Data Science offers a wide range of exciting career opportunities. Here are some common job roles in the field:
        ul
          li Data Scientist: Analyze large datasets to derive insights and make data-driven decisions.
          li Machine Learning Engineer: Build and train machine learning models for predictive analytics.
          li Data Analyst: Interpret data to provide actionable recommendations.
          li Business Intelligence Analyst: Create visualizations and reports to support business decisions.
          li Data Engineer: Develop and maintain data pipelines for efficient data processing.
          li AI Researcher: Conduct research to advance artificial intelligence algorithms.

        p.large-font
          | Whether you're interested in finance, healthcare, e-commerce, or any other industry, data science skills are in high demand.

    .row.future-of-data-science
      .col-lg-12
        h2(style="color: white;") The Future of Data Science
        p.large-font
          | Data Science is at the forefront of technological innovation. With the growing volume of data, the field is expected to continue evolving, offering new opportunities for data professionals. As businesses increasingly rely on data for decision-making, the relevance of data science is on the rise.

    .row.get-started
      .col-lg-12
        h2(style="color: white;") Ready to Dive into Data Science?
        p.large-font
          | If you're intrigued by the world of data and analytics and want to pursue a career in data science, there are numerous resources and educational programs available to help you get started. Embrace the future of data-driven insights with Data Science!
